Hello from Anannas! Anannas is a unified API gateway that simplifies access to over 500 large language models (LLMs) from various providers, including OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google. By consolidating these models into a single, high-performance interface, Anannas eliminates integration complexity, ensures reliability, and reduces operational costs through intelligent orchestration. ([aitoolnet.com](https://www.aitoolnet.com/anannas?utm_source=openai))

With Anannas, developers can achieve maximum availability and efficiency through automatic load balancing and provider selection. The platform routes requests based on criteria such as lowest price, fastest latency, or highest throughput, and includes built-in fallback support. If a preferred provider fails, Anannas automatically switches to a healthy alternative with zero downtime. ([aitoolnet.com](https://www.aitoolnet.com/anannas?utm_source=openai))

Anannas is fully compatible with the official OpenAI SDK. By pointing the base URL to Anannas and using your Anannas API key, you can seamlessly integrate various LLMs into your applications. ([docs.anannas.ai](https://docs.anannas.ai/?utm_source=openai))

Additionally, Anannas supports streaming responses from any model, including OpenAI and Anthropic. This feature is particularly useful for building chat interfaces where the UI updates as the model generates output in real time. ([docs.anannas.ai](https://docs.anannas.ai/API/Streaming?utm_source=openai))
